Binary version of libedit3 compiled from
http://www.thrysoee.dk/editline/
The headers and binaries were moved to the libedit-3.1 directory

Make sure you have these packages if you're trying to build chroot:

sudo apt-get install libncurses5-dev
sudo apt-get install groff-base

Otherwise it will most likely build but crash when you try to use it...
